{"tid":2029651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明報：香港眾志有成員被捕控以「違反商品說明條例」 據悉與其出售口罩有關！","createTime":"2020-05-22T10:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T10:41:20.000Z","uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9a87334891664e451c1dd8fff066eb0d69e2077e","tid":2029651,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319e867ec878e60bf85b3e4ed36fcfec06f987b6","tid":2029651,"uid":63113,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:36:36.000Z","msg":"據了解，海關早前拘捕一名香港眾志成員，涉嫌在早前出售口罩時違反《商品說明條例》。香港眾志主席林朗彥向本報確認，有一名眾志成員被海關拘捕，詳情稍後交代。海關確認於新蒲崗拘捕一名24歲男子，並檢獲935盒涉嫌違反《商品說明條例》的外科口罩、每盒35片裝，共32,725片外科口罩，市值約9.35萬元。<br />\n<br />\n海關指出，早前接獲舉報，指有網上商戶透過餐廳食肆供應一款附有「NOT MADE IN CHINA」、「ASTM Level 1」、「BFE&ge;95%」、「Fluid Resistance」及「PFE&ge;95%」標示的外科口罩，懷疑附有虛假產地及效能聲稱。海關接報後採取試購行動，並展開跟進調查。<br />\n<br />\n海關把試購所得樣本送往化驗所作含菌量測試，測試結果證實樣本符合含菌量標準。然而，由於該商戶一直未能提供認證，證明相關口罩符合所作的標示聲稱，遂採取執法行動。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志早前稱蒐羅到逾百萬個口罩，首批每盒35片裝，會以成本價100元與「黃店」合作售賣。眾志早前稱，因為怕有人去當地「搶貨」，拒絕透露口罩來源地，只在盒上以英文寫「非中國製造」（NOT MADE IN CHINA）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200522/s00001/1590142383581/%e8%b3%a3%e5%8f%a3%e7%bd%a9%e6%b6%89%e9%81%95%e5%95%86%e5%93%81%e8%aa%aa%e6%98%8e%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b-%e7%9c%be%e5%bf%97%e4%b8%80%e6%88%90%e5%93%a1%e8%a2%ab%e6%8d%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200522%2Fs00001%2F1590142383581%2F%25e8%25b3%25a3%25e5%258f%25a3%25e7%25bd%25a9%25e6%25b6%2589%25e9%2581%2595%25e5%2595%2586%25e5%2593%2581%25e8%25aa%25aa%25e6%2598%258e%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b-%25e7%259c%25be%25e5%25bf%2597%25e4%25b8%2580%25e6%2588%2590%25e5%2593%25a1%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258d%2595&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSsLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=48cec602\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200522%2Fs00001%2F1590142383581%2F%25e8%25b3%25a3%25e5%258f%25a3%25e7%25bd%25a9%25e6%25b6%2589%25e9%2581%2595%25e5%2595%2586%25e5%2593%2581%25e8%25aa%25aa%25e6%2598%258e%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b-%25e7%259c%25be%25e5%25bf%2597%25e4%25b8%2580%25e6%2588%2590%25e5%2593%25a1%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258d%2595&h=eee7609e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200522/s00001/1590142383581/%e8%b3%a3%e5%8f%a3%e7%bd%a9%e6%b6%89%e9%81%95%e5%95%86%e5%93%81%e8%aa%aa%e6%98%8e%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b-%e7%9c%be%e5%bf%97%e4%b8%80%e6%88%90%e5%93%a1%e8%a2%ab%e6%8d%95</a>"},{"pid":"3950e72b851fb116655f422731c93ad7feebcbb2","tid":2029651,"uid":69221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:37:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tFRAOtS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtFRAOtS.jpg&h=65c4fe9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4f61f0dd09e012f3eb14ea33e46d1b77f9e32f1","tid":2029651,"uid":69221,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3950e72b851fb116655f422731c93ad7feebcbb2","tid":2029651,"uid":69221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:37:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tFRAOtS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtFRAOtS.jpg&h=65c4fe9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:39:18.000Z","msg":"戴教授呢排算洗心革面，唔計"},{"pid":"eb581c10329c657815c975fbadea8857785e35c7","tid":2029651,"uid":219156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:40:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8f2bd636a5373cf50bec6a96a304e2adaa51ee0a","tid":2029651,"uid":189157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:40:26.000Z","msg":"海關前線好黃"},{"pid":"118c80cab1097e3e8b93418d34f7a5d22524ee23","tid":2029651,"uid":219156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f2bd636a5373cf50bec6a96a304e2adaa51ee0a","tid